  succeeded by jared cohon referencesedit fenton edwin  carnegie mellon  a centennial history pittsburgh carnegie mellon university press isbn   v t e presidents of carnegie mellon university arthur hamerschlag  thomas baker  robert doherty  john warner  guyford stever  richard cyert  robert mehrabian  jared cohon  subra suresh  farnam jahanian interim  this biography of an american academic administrator is a stub you can help wikipedia by expanding it v t e this pittsburghrelated article is a stub you can help wikipedia by expanding it v t e retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlerobertmehrabianoldid categories presidents of carnegie mellon universityamerican university and college presidents birthsliving peopleamerican people of armenian descentamerican people of iranian descentmassachusetts institute of technology alumniuniversity of illinois at urbana–champaign facultyuniversity of california santa barbara facultyiranian emigrants to the united statespeople from tehraniranian armenian peoplephillips exeter academy alumnippg peoplemembers of the united states national academy of engineeringiranian expatriate academicsamerican academic administrator stubspittsburgh stubshidden categories articles lacking intext citations from february all articles lacking intext citationsall stub articles navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages فارسی edit links this page was last edited on  june  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license additional terms may ap